data.text:
67 Metascore

2001

1 hr 47 mins

Drama

R

Watchlist

Where to Watch

Anna Friel and Michelle Williams give very effective performances in screenwriter-director Sandra Goldbacher's smart and sincere drama about the lifelong friendship between two suburban London gals. One is carefree and outgoing (Friel); the other more reserved and grounded (Williams). Also playing a major role are the changing fashions and music of the 1970s and '80s. Kyle MacLachlan.
